name: Fairuz
description: They’re all about bringing exquisite food that will satisfy their customers’ cravings for Persian cuisine. With the true meaning of “Fairuz” - triumphant, they serve their customers like royalty.

name: Mana
description: Sophisticated cravings. Refreshing flavors. “Tita food”. - Sandwiched. Experience a unique blend of elegance and and punch, with meals that serve you heaven on a platter.

name: Taverna
description: Taking influence from the greek voyagers who sought out local tavernas for food and lodging, Taverna provides a quick and authentic greek cuisine for the weary student traversing their academic life.
